**Topic** : Artificial General Intelligence

![](data:image/png;base64,)

**Article Source** :

- **[What is artificial general intelligence (AGI)?](https://cloud.google.com/discover/what-is-artificial-general-intelligence)**
- Research Paper - **[Artificial General Intelligence: Concept, State of the Art, and Future Prospects](https://www.researchgate.net/publication/271390398_Artificial_General_Intelligence_Concept_State_of_the_Art_and_Future_Prospects)**

**TL;DR** :

Artificial general intelligence (AGI) refers to the hypothetical intelligence of a machine that possesses the ability to understand or learn any intellectual task that a human being can. It is a type of[artificial intelligence](https://cloud.google.com/learn/what-is-artificial-intelligence)(AI) that aims to mimic the cognitive abilities of the human brain.
